      "duration": 1.03,
      "size": 16416,
      "text": "欢迎来到信号处理实验。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "signal-processing",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/signal-processing/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.11,
      "size": 33696,
      "text": "你每天都在与信号打交道：听音乐、打电话、看视频。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "signal-processing",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/signal-processing/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.65,
      "size": 26352,
      "text": "这些信号是如何被处理、传输和存储的？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "signal-processing",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-4",
      "filename": "intro-intro-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/signal-processing/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.4,
      "size": 22464,
      "text": "信号处理正是研究这些问题的学科。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "signal-processing",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-1",
      "filename": "concept-concept-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/signal-processing/xiaoxiao/concept-concept-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.29,
      "size": 20592,
      "text": "信号可以在时域或频域中分析。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "signal-processing",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-2",
      "filename": "concept-concept-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/signal-processing/xiaoxiao/concept-concept-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.3,
      "size": 36864,
      "text": "时域显示信号随时间的变化，频域显示信号包含的频率成分。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "signal-processing",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-3",
      "filename": "concept-concept-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/signal-processing/xiaoxiao/concept-concept-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.5,
      "size": 24048,
      "text": "傅里叶变换是连接时域和频域的桥梁。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "signal-processing",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-4",
      "filename": "concept-concept-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/signal-processing/xiaoxiao/concept-concept-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.29,
      "size": 20592,
      "text": "让我们通过实例来理解这些概念。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "signal-processing",
      "section_id": "sampling",
      "line_id": "samp-1",
      "filename": "sampling-samp-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/signal-processing/xiaoxiao/sampling-samp-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.28,
      "size": 20448,
      "text": "数字信号是对连续信号的采样。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "signal-processing",
      "section_id": "sampling",
      "line_id": "samp-2",
      "filename": "sampling-samp-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/signal-processing/xiaoxiao/sampling-samp-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.19,
      "size": 34992,
      "text": "采样定理告诉我们：采样频率必须大于信号最高频率的两倍。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "signal-processing",
      "section_id": "sampling",
      "line_id": "samp-3",
      "filename": "sampling-samp-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/signal-processing/xiaoxiao/sampling-samp-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.59,
      "size": 25488,
      "text": "否则会产生混叠，无法正确恢复原信号。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "signal-processing",
      "section_id": "sampling",
      "line_id": "samp-4",
      "filename": "sampling-samp-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/signal-processing/xiaoxiao/sampling-samp-4.mp3",
      "duration": 3.19,
      "size": 50976,
      "text": "这就是为什么CD的采样率是44.1kHz，因为人耳能听到的最高频率约20kHz。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "signal-processing",
      "section_id": "filter",
      "line_id": "filt-1",
      "filename": "filter-filt-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/signal-processing/xiaoxiao/filter-filt-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.84,
      "size": 29376,
      "text": "滤波器用于选择性地保留或去除某些频率成分。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "signal-processing",
      "section_id": "filter",
      "line_id": "filt-2",
      "filename": "filter-filt-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/signal-processing/xiaoxiao/filter-filt-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.81,
      "size": 28944,
      "text": "低通滤波器保留低频，去除高频，用于去噪。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "signal-processing",
      "section_id": "filter",
      "line_id": "filt-3",
      "filename": "filter-filt-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/signal-processing/xiaoxiao/filter-filt-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.99,
      "size": 31824,
      "text": "高通滤波器保留高频，去除低频，用于边缘检测。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "signal-processing",
      "section_id": "filter",
      "line_id": "filt-4",
      "filename": "filter-filt-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/signal-processing/xiaoxiao/filter-filt-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.95,
      "size": 31248,
      "text": "带通滤波器只保留特定频率范围，用于信号分离。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "signal-processing",
      "section_id": "application",
      "line_id": "app-1",
      "filename": "application-app-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/signal-processing/xiaoxiao/application-app-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.45,
      "size": 23184,
      "text": "信号处理在现代技术中无处不在。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "signal-processing",
      "section_id": "application",
      "line_id": "app-2",
      "filename": "application-app-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/signal-processing/xiaoxiao/application-app-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.47,
      "size": 23472,
      "text": "音频处理：降噪、均衡、压缩。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "signal-processing",
      "section_id": "application",
      "line_id": "app-3",
      "filename": "application-app-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/signal-processing/xiaoxiao/application-app-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.59,
      "size": 25488,
      "text": "图像处理：锐化、模糊、边缘检测。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "signal-processing",
      "section_id": "application",
      "line_id": "app-4",
      "filename": "application-app-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/signal-processing/xiaoxiao/application-app-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.43,
      "size": 22896,
      "text": "通信系统：调制、解调、编码。"
    },
    {
